				<wikidot:authorName>Demetersson</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3856010</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>To be brutally honest, this article isn't even very funny. And even if it was, it would fit better as a -j. I'm not against funny articles being in the main series (Bush vs. Gore, Megalomania, &quot;Fuck off Carl&quot;, etc) but I still expect some sort of story or creative concept with them.</p> <p>Overall it's a -1.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
